<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login – Painel Admin Notícias 360</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        :root {
            --red: #E30614;
            --red-dark: #b8040f;
            --blue: #004796;
            --blue-dark: #003370;
            --gray-900: #111827;
            --gray-700: #374151;
            --gray-500: #6b7280;
            --gray-300: #d1d5db;
            --gray-100: #f3f4f6;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            background: var(--gray-100);
        }

        /* ─── Painel esquerdo (formulário) ─── */
        .left-panel {
            flex: 0 0 480px;
            background: var(--white);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 3rem 3rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            box-shadow: 4px 0 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        }

        .logo-wrap {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .logo-wrap img {
            height: 52px;
            width: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .form-header {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .form-header h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--gray-900);
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-header p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--gray-500);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .form-header p span {
            color: var(--red);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
        }

        .divider::before,
        .divider::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--gray-300);
        }

        .divider span {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--gray-500);
            white-space: nowrap;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Formulário */
        form {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .field {
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-700);
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.01em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .input-wrap {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-wrap svg {
            position: absolute;
            left: 0.9rem;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--gray-400, #9ca3af);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem 0.75rem 2.6rem;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-300);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-family: inherit;
            color: var(--gray-900);
            background: var(--white);
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--red);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(227, 6, 20, 0.1);
        }

        input::placeholder {
            color: #9ca3af;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.85rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            background: var(--red);
            color: var(--white);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: inherit;
            cursor: pointer;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            transition: background .2s, transform .1s, box-shadow .2s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(227, 6, 20, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background: var(--red-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(227, 6, 20, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-submit:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }

        .error-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            color: #b91c1c;
            padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .footer-link {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.75rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--gray-500);
        }

        .footer-link a {
            color: var(--blue);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer-link a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* ─── Painel direito (imagem / decorativo) ─── */
        .right-panel {
            flex: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #004796 0%, #001f45 60%, #1a0005 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Círculos decorativos */
        .right-panel::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(227, 6, 20, 0.12);
            top: -150px;
            right: -150px;
        }

        .right-panel::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 350px;
            height: 350px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255, 0.04);
            bottom: -80px;
            left: -80px;
        }

        .right-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 420px;
        }

        .right-logo {
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .right-logo img {
            height: 70px;
            width: auto;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .right-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .right-content h2 em {
            font-style: normal;
            color: #fca5a5;
        }

        .right-content p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Grid de stats */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255, 0.07);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
            text-align: left;
            backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        }

        .stat-card .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        .stat-card .stat-value span {
            color: #fca5a5;
        }

        .stat-card .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255, 0.55);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Responsivo */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            body {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .right-panel {
                display: none;
            }

            .left-panel {
                flex: 1;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .left-panel {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- ─── LADO ESQUERDO: Formulário ─── -->
    <div class="left-panel">

        <div class="logo-wrap">
            <img src="/uploads/logo-noticias360.webp" alt="Notícias +360">
        </div>

        <div class="form-header">
            <h1>Bem-vindo ao Painel</h1>
            <p>Acesse com suas credenciais para gerenciar o conteúdo da <span>Notícias +360</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"><span>Acesso restrito</span></div>

        <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
        <div class="error-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
            </svg>
            <%= error %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="post" action="/admin/login">
            <div class="field">
                <label for="identifier">E-mail ou usuário</label>
                <div class="input-wrap">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
                    </svg>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="identifier"
                        name="identifier"
                        placeholder="seu@email.com ou usuário"
                        required
                        autocomplete="username"
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
                <label for="password">Senha</label>
                <div class="input-wrap">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
                    </svg>
                    <input
                        type="password"
                        id="password"
                        name="password"
                        placeholder="••••••••"
                        required
                        autocomplete="current-password"
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Entrar no Painel</button>
        </form>

        <div class="footer-link">
            <a href="/">← Voltar à API</a>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ─── LADO DIREITO: Decorativo ─── -->
    <div class="right-panel">
        <div class="right-content">
            <div class="right-logo">
                <img src="/uploads/logo-noticias360.webp" alt="Notícias +360">
            </div>

            <h2>O portal de notícias que <em>conecta</em> sua cidade</h2>
            <p>Gerencie todo o conteúdo editorial — notícias, categorias, mídias e muito mais — em um painel centralizado e intuitivo.</p>

            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-value">360<span>°</span></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Cobertura completa</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-value">24<span>/7</span></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Publicação contínua</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-value">100<span>%</span></div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Conteúdo local</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <div class="stat-value">∞</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Possibilidades editoriais</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
